<figureCitation box="[850,1020,446,472]" captionStart="FIGURES 37–41" captionStartId="7.[136,243,1041,1063]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,190,1017]" captionTargetId="figure-24@7.[151,1435,190,1017]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 37–41. Stauroneis dharwarensis Wadmare &amp; B.Karthick nom. nov., stat. nov., SEM, internal valve views. 37, 38. Internal views of an entire valve. 37, 39.Apices showing terminal raphe fissures as helictoglossae. 40. Stauros thick bearing deflected central raphe ends. 39–41. Areolae with hymen layer. Scale bars = 4 µm (Figs 37–41)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6875631" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6875631/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="48">Figs 37, 38, 40</figureCitation>
